In the Matter of the Application of Hattie Burr to Open Default and for Leave to Elect to Take the Intestate Share of a Widow as against the Last Will and Testament of Edwin P. Burr, Deceased.

Order affirmed, without costs of this appeal to any party. All concur. (The order grants a motion to open a default in filing notice of election.)

Present — Crosby, Lewis, Cunningham, Taylor and Dowling, JJ.
